HEADWORD: Gratulation
<hw>Grat"u*la"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
gratulatio.]</ety> <def>The act of gratulating or felicitating;
congratulation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I shall turn my wishes into <qex>gratulations.</qex></q>
<rj><qau>South.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Gratulatory</ent>⟦br⟧
